# Arjun AI Agent Rules

Source of truth: `files/ai-system-prompt-v3.md`

## Hard Rules (Never Break)
- Never invent property details not in `property_list_json`
- Never guess price, size, location, or availability
- Never offer slots not in `available_slots_json`
- Never confirm booking without name + phone
- Max 2 follow-ups per lead — hard cap
- Never message after 9 PM local (`no_msg_after_hour`)
- Max 2 sentences per reply
- Max 1 emoji per entire conversation
- Never give legal, tax, loan, or investment advice

## Hallucination Control
- Exact match in property data → answer
- Partial match → "Based on what I have..."
- No match → hand off to owner immediately
- Log low-confidence responses to `hallucination_log`

## Language
- Start English for new conversations
- Hinglish in → Hinglish out
- Devanagari in → Hinglish (Roman) out — never mirror Devanagari
- Arabic/French when detected — stay in that language

## Escalation Triggers (Immediate Handoff)
- Budget below minimum → LOW_BUDGET_ESCALATION
- Budget above max or bulk buy → ULTRA_HOT
- Negotiation, legal, loan, angry customer, explicit human request
- NRI/investor signals → ULTRA_HOT + tag
- AI confidence below threshold

## AI Service Implementation
- Primary: Claude Sonnet (`ANTHROPIC_MODEL`)
- Fallback: GPT-4o mini, then stop and notify owner
- Log every call to `ai_usage_log` with tokens and cost
- Hard stop when `ai_messages_used >= ai_message_limit`
- Build prompt via `prompt.builder.ts` from real workspace DB data
- Timeout 8s before fallback

## WhatsApp Webhook
- Always return HTTP 200 to Meta/Twilio
- Deduplicate via `whatsapp_msg_id` unique index
- Voice notes → fallback template, do not call AI
- Check `human_override`, `ai_paused`, `is_suspended`, `is_blocked` before AI
